# PouchCare OS — Cursor AI Context

## Project
Full-stack agency management system.
CEO: Abdullah Al Mamun | MD (Co-MD): Md Oliullah | Ops: Md. Habibullah

## Git
Remote: https://gitlab.com/Pouchcare/OS (SSH: `git@gitlab.com:Pouchcare/OS.git`). CI/CD: `.gitlab-ci.yml`. SSH setup: `docs/gitlab-ssh.md`.  
Branch from develop. Never push directly to main.

## Tech Stack
- API: Node.js 20, Express 5, TypeScript, Prisma ORM, PostgreSQL, Redis, WebSocket
- Frontend: React 18, Vite 5, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 3, TanStack Query v5, Zustand v4
- Auth: JWT HS256 (15min access / 7d refresh), 2FA TOTP for CEO + CO_MD

## Domains & Ports
- api.pouchcare.com     → apps/api/           (port 7000 — PM2)
- m.pouchcare.com       → apps/management/    (port 5174 dev)
- office.pouchcare.com  → apps/office/        (port 5175 dev)
- my.pouchcare.com      → apps/client-portal/ (port 5176 dev)
- pouchcare.com         → apps/landing/       (static HTML)

ALL server paths under: /home/pouchcare/htdocs/

