## Key Files
- apps/api/src/server.ts          — Express server, all 30 routes mounted
- apps/api/src/routes/            — 33 route files
- apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma   — 32 tables, all enums, all relations
- apps/api/src/lib/response.ts    — ok(), created(), serverError(), etc.
- apps/api/src/lib/pagination.ts  — getPaginationParams(), buildMeta()
- apps/api/src/middleware/auth.ts — authenticate, isCEO, isOps, isManager, isHR
- ecosystem.config.js             — PM2: PORT=7000
- deploy.sh                       — Full first-deploy script
- deploy/nginx/                   — 5 Nginx configs
- deploy/update.sh                — Re-deploy script

## Roles (actual Prisma enum values)
CEO | CO_MD | OP_MANAGER | HR_MANAGER | BRANCH_MANAGER | STAFF | INTERN

## Role Groups (middleware/auth.ts)
- isCEO      = CEO + CO_MD
- isOps      = CEO + CO_MD + OP_MANAGER
- isManager  = CEO + CO_MD + OP_MANAGER + BRANCH_MANAGER
- isHR       = CEO + CO_MD + OP_MANAGER + HR_MANAGER
- requirePortal = portal members only (type: 'portal')

## Important Prisma Field Names
- StaffMember.lastLoginAt (NOT lastLoginDate)
- PortalMember.lastLoginDate (NOT lastLoginAt)
- StaffMember.totpSecret (NOT twoFactorSecret)
- Attendance.staffMemberId (NOT memberId)
- LeaveRequest.staffMemberId (NOT memberId)
- DailyReport.staffMemberId (NOT memberId)
- PortalMember.referredById (NOT referrerId)
- Commission.earnerId (NOT referrerId)
- Commission.commissionAmountUsd (NOT commissionAmount)
- WalletTransaction.balanceAfterUsd (NOT balanceAfter)
- Domain.domainName (NOT name)
- PortalMember.resetTokenExpiry (NOT resetPasswordExpires)

## ApprovalStatus Enum Values
WAITING | SUBMITTED | APPROVED_MGR | REJECTED_MGR | ESCALATED | VERIFIED

## Response Helpers (lib/response.ts)
- ok(res, data, meta?)
- created(res, data)
- paginated(res, data[], {total,page,limit,totalPages})
- serverError(res, err?) — accepts unknown catch errors
- buildMeta(total, page, limit) → meta object

## Dev Setup
cd apps/api && cp .env.example .env
# Set: DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET (32+), JWT_REFRESH_SECRET (32+)
npm install && npx prisma generate && npx prisma migrate dev && npm run db:seed
npm run dev  # → localhost:7000

